business_description.Business Description:
The Official Trump Token, also known as TRUMP, is a meme token launched by President-elect Donald Trump on his Truth Social account. Built on the Solana blockchain, TRUMP is a meme coin that allows users to trade and invest while embracing its connection to the President’s political legacy.

TRUMP, like other meme coins, experiences high volatility due to its speculative nature and its success primarily relies on its community-driven growth and social media buzz.

Experimental Crypto assets might be riskier than other crypto assets and require careful consideration. Further details of these risks may be found here.

Stay up to date on the share price of TRUMP by adding it to your eToro watchlist.
